- Multiply the new reading time by the number of pages read per day.
Number of pages read per day = 3 hours x 100 pages = 300 pages per day

- Multiply the number of pages read per day by the number of days in a week.
Number of pages read per week = 300 pages per day x 7 days = 2100 pages per week

**Answer:**
